<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>An event B07 indicates that a health professional is granted a certificate/permission for a special purpose. A permission is issued by an organization and documented in form of a certificate. An update of a role results in an issuing of a new certificate.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The EVN segment is used to indicate the effective or planned date.</p>
</div>
